  allLines:
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dc24e77c8220d5b43bd418e911809b3b, type: 3}
    sentence: "You know, I have to be honest here. I actually never thought I\u2019d
      meet someone like you in a program like this."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 1936918675910826544, guid: e8f1130d0e09cef45bb1f9ab49489848, type: 3}
    sentence: Likewise. I thought I was going to be meeting a bunch of clueless people
      who are just here for an easy hook-up.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Oh, you weren\u2019t looking for a hook-up then?"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "That.. is not what I said. I see what you\u2019re trying to do here."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Does it bother you? I can stop.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "No, not at all. I have to warn you, though. I\u2019m probably not
      what you think I am."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "What if that\u2019s exactly what I want? Someone who isn\u2019t at
      all what they seem."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Do you want something different than what you see right now?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Linus
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 
    eventTrigger: 
    choices:
    - choices: "What if I want both what I see and what I don\u2019t?"
